rod. The slider moves along the z-axis of the slidersite frame. Therefore the site should be oriented as needed when
it is defined in the kinematic tree; its orientation cannot be changed in the actuator definition.</xs:documentation>
                    </xs:annotation>
                  </xs:attribute>
